  "title": "pessimisticUpdate",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/router-store/data-persistence/src/operators.ts?message=docs(router-store)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L122\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/16.0.0-beta.0/modules/router-store/data-persistence/src/operators.ts#L55-L122\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io/api/router-store\", \"name\": \"@ngrx/router-store\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io/api/router-store/data-persistence\", \"name\": \"@ngrx/router-store/data-persistence\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://ngrx.io/api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate\", \"name\": \"pessimisticUpdate\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/router-store\">@ngrx/router-store</a> > <a href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence\">@ngrx/router-store/data-persistence</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"pessimisticupdate\">pessimisticUpdate<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate#pessimisticupdate\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Handles pessimistic updates (updating the server first).</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate\" class=\"code-anchor\">pessimisticUpdate</a></span>&#x3C;T extends Array&#x3C;unknown>, A extends <a href=\"api/store/Action\" class=\"code-anchor\">Action</a>>(opts: PessimisticUpdateOpts&#x3C;T, A>)</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"opts\"></a>\n        <code>opts</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>PessimisticUpdateOpts&#x3C;T, A></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Updating the server, when implemented naively, suffers from race conditions and poor error handling.</p>\n<p><code><a href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate\" class=\"code-anchor\">pessimisticUpdate</a></code> addresses these problems. It runs all fetches in order, which removes race conditions\nand forces the developer to handle errors.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@Injectable()\nclass TodoEffects {\n  updateTodo$ = <a href=\"api/effects/createEffect\" class=\"code-anchor\">createEffect</a>(() =>\n    this.actions$.pipe(\n      <a href=\"api/effects/ofType\" class=\"code-anchor\">ofType</a>('UPDATE_TODO'),\n      <a href=\"api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate\" class=\"code-anchor\">pessimisticUpdate</a>({\n        // provides an action\n        run: (action: UpdateTodo) => {\n          // update the backend first, and then dispatch an action that will\n          // update the client side\n          return this.backend.updateTodo(action.todo.id, action.todo).pipe(\n            map((updated) => ({\n              type: 'UPDATE_TODO_SUCCESS',\n              todo: updated,\n            }))\n          );\n        },\n        onError: (action: UpdateTodo, error: any) => {\n          // we don't need to undo the changes <a href=\"api/store/on\" class=\"code-anchor\">on</a> the client side.\n          // we can dispatch an error, or simply log the error here and return `null`\n          return null;\n        },\n      })\n    )\n  );\n\n  constructor(private actions$: <a href=\"api/effects/Actions\" class=\"code-anchor\">Actions</a>, private backend: Backend) {}\n}\n</code-example>\n<p>Note that if you don't return a new action from the run callback, you must set the dispatch property\nof the effect to false, like this:</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\nclass TodoEffects {\n  updateTodo$ = <a href=\"api/effects/createEffect\" class=\"code-anchor\">createEffect</a>(() =>\n    this.actions$.pipe(\n      //...\n    ), { dispatch: false }\n  );\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/router-store/data-persistence\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/effects/Actions\n - api/effects/createEffect\n - api/effects/ofType\n - api/router-store\n - api/router-store/data-persistence\n - api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate#description\n - api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate#pessimisticupdate\n - api/router-store/data-persistence/pessimisticUpdate#usage-notes\n - api/store/Action\n - api/store/on\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/modules/router-store/data-persistence/src/operators.ts?message=docs(router-store)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L55-L122\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/tree/16.0.0-beta.0/modules/router-store/data-persistence/src/operators.ts#L55-L122\n-->"
